Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:23.80,Main - Top + Italics,Ferry Announcement,0,0,0,,We will now be arriving at Torishirojima \NFishing Port, Torishirojima Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:28.46,Main - Top + Italics,Ferry Announcement,0,0,0,,We may experience a strong \Nimpact upon docking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:31.04,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Torishirojima, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:32.11,Main - Top + Italics,Ferry Announcement,0,0,0,,Please remain seated until further notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:46.40,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Guess this makes me a wounded bird of passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:48.01,Default,Kido's Grandmother,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:55.88,Default,Kido's Grandmother,0,0,0,,Who's a wounded bird of passage?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:57.59,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:00:59.93,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:01.34,Default,Kido's Grandmother,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:02.40,Default,Kido's Grandmother,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:07.44,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Because I'm hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:08.72,Default,Kido's Grandmother,0,0,0,,Hurt where?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:10.36,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,My heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:13.83,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,F-Forget I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:03.33,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,This is my first time on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:05.05,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Why does it feel so nostalgic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:05.91,Default,Kido's Grandmother,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:09.61,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Ah, whoops, I was thinking out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:11.00,Default,Kido's Grandmother,0,0,0,,Quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:18.60,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Have you ever gone somewhere that felt\Nnostalgic even though you'd never been before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:21.22,Default,Kido's Grandmother,0,0,0,,Oh, it's that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:28.60,Default,Kido's Grandmother,0,0,0,,A hijab.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:30.54,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:35.45,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You mean deja vu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:37.09,Default,Kido's Grandmother,0,0,0,,That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:38.61,Default,Kido's Grandmother,0,0,0,,Hijab.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:52.94,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.13,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.85,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:41.02,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,I'd planned to pick you \Nup at the port, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:45.57,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Anyway, again, I'm Misaki Kyouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:49.74,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,I've been taking care of the house\N since Grandma passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:51.94,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Takahara Hairi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:54.72,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I appreciate you looking\N after me over summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.42,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,I'll show you to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:00.25,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Sorry about the musty smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:04.13,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,I did give it a clean, but it's been \Na storage room for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:08.02,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,No, it's a perfect reflection \Nof my emotional state.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:12.48,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,After all, I'm a wounded bird of passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:13.41,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.44,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:20.50,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Oh, right, I have another \Nrelative here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.11,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Family, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:23.38,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.50,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Feels like she's always out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:26.99,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,She isn't here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:29.45,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:42.40,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,"Want to come to Torishirojima Island?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:48.88,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,So read the letter I received from \NAuntie Kyouko just before summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:52.35,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,My eccentric grandmother passed last month,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:57.89,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,leaving behind a shed full of things\Nshe'd collected while traveling the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:02.11,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Some of it's of sentimental \Nvalue to our family,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:05.31,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,so we can't just call on a cleaning company.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:11.12,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Accordingly, Auntie Kyouko was looking\Nfor a relative with some time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.76,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,I happened to fit the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:18.59,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Though I never had a day to spare\Nuntil last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:52.79,Main - Top + Italics,TV,0,0,0,,And now, the weather for tomorrow, July 26th.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:56.79,Main - Top + Italics,TV,0,0,0,,The Setouchi region will see high pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:56.79,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.66,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Have you gotten any rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.64,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Sorry to bug you right off the bat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.23,Main - Top + Italics,TV,0,0,0,,Sanuki udon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.06,Main - Top + Italics,TV,0,0,0,,With a massive helping of kakiage tempura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.10,Main - Top + Italics,TV,0,0,0,,That light broth and smooth texture!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:11.68,Main - Top + Italics,TV,0,0,0,,It's Sanuki udon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:15.85,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnImpact\fs20\shad1\pos(177.913,79.347)\frz344\c&HD9E3DC&\3c&H4F70B1&\4c&H607895&}Sun Curry Golden
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:15.85,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\shad1\bord1\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\b1\c&H979F9C&\3c&H22263D&\4c&H3A3B6D&\pos(231.195,203.633)}Sanuki Udon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:15.85,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\shad1\bord1\fax.4\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\b1\c&HDDE3DE&\3c&H454555&\4c&H6873B2&\pos(354.296,64.041)\frz17.4}Sanuki Udon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:15.85,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,I wish this didn't have \Nto be your first meal here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:18.18,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:19.51,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:24.98,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,I would have cooked for you, but y'know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:28.56,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:29.86,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:30.84,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.57,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! There's a nice place nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.84,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Hairi-kun, can you ride a scooter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:39.84,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I have a license, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:44.49,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,There's a dining hall down the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:46.24,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,The food there is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:49.84,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fay.13\fnArial\b1\fs12\shad0\pos(180.976,185.878)\c&H98A0BA&\3c&H69546A&}Marin Diner
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:56.60,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnArial\fs14\shad0\bord0\b1\frz344.1\pos(206.794,8.939)\c&H404B4B&}Katsudon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:56.60,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnArial\fs14\shad0\bord0\b1\frz344.1\c&H404B4B&\pos(173.722,64.653)}Cream Bun Meal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:56.60,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnArial\fs16\shad0\bord0\b1\frz344.1\c&H404B4B&\pos(155.349,120.98)}Happy Combo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:56.60,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnArial\fs16\shad0\bord0\b1\frz344.1\c&H404B4B&\pos(135.139,179.755)}Morning Combo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:56.60,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnArial\fs16\shad0\bord0\b1\frz344.1\c&H404B4B&\pos(119.827,233.021)}Lunch Combo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:56.60,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,They have...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:08:00.10,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'd like the Happy Combo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:02.70,Default,Shop,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:15.82,Default,Shop,0,0,0,,Here y'are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:24.00,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:28.34,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I thought I ordered the Happy Combo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:30.92,Default,Shop,0,0,0,,The chicken and its egg died together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:31.80,Default,Shop,0,0,0,,Happy, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:45.06,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Guess I'll do a lap around the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:13.42,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(119,1)\pos(318.775,74.449)\blur1\fnTimes New Roman\fs14\shad0\b1\c&H6E7064&\3c&H322613&}Torishirojima\NElementary
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:15.68,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Ah, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:17.91,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm completely lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:09:58.91,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:17.95,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:19.79,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:23.12,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Takahara Hairi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:25.54,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Taka...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:27.54,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.32,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.13,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Shiroha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:41.88,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shiroha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.64,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:45.84,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:47.60,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Swimming?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.33,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should be asking questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:53.90,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:00.40,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,So you're lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:03.06,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm trying to get back to Katou-san's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:06.19,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Don't you mean your place, Sakahara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:08.62,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it's Takahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:11.16,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,S-Sakahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:11.98,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:15.58,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Okay, Sakahara is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:26.39,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Sorry, I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:30.10,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Up the hill and right at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.27,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Take a left at the third crossroads.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:37.67,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.37,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.32,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Why are you practicing at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:46.40,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You shouldn't. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:48.45,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What if you get a leg cramp\Nwhen no one's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:49.30,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,...koi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:51.20,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Dosukoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:56.96,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,B-Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:59.36,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Thanks for the directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:14.27,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:16.26,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.56,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:20.44,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was surprisingly good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:24.78,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,By the way, what's "dosukoi" about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:26.43,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Incessant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:28.70,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Oh, er, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:33.54,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,No, it's like a thing people say around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:37.08,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,When someone's being incessant \Nor annoying, you say "dosukoi."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:38.34,Flashback - Italics,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Lay off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:40.39,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.34,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,So I was being annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:46.25,Main - Top + Italics,TV,0,0,0,,It's a walk-off grand slam comeback!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.93,Main - Top + Italics,TV,0,0,0,,He knocks it out of the park!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:12:59.61,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.94,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Get up, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:12.57,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,It's already eight in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:14.40,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You're, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:16.62,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Umi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:20.91,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You must be the other relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:22.68,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm Takahara Hairi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:23.55,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.82,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Pleased to make your acquaintance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:27.98,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Takahara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.85,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Please, dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:33.35,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Fried rice? First thing in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.80,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,I made it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:38.59,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Wow, that's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:41.52,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.43,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:43.61,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:45.47,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:47.14,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.54,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Okay, let's dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:50.70,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:55.50,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:59.46,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,The rice is so fluffy, \Nand it's seasoned just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:58.65,Main - Top,Umi,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:05.42,Default,Umi; Hairi,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.83,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,I lost again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:10.14,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,You're cheating!
