Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.55,0:14:12.73,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,How could I cheat at rock paper scissors?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.73,0:14:15.47,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,There's no way I could lose so many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.61,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:19.38,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}are{\i0} cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.71,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It isn't cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.77,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It's written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:27.59,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You make this "hnnngh" face \Nwhen you throw rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:30.97,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,And you make this "skreee" face \Nwhen you throw scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You're so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:35.77,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Hang on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:39.86,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,So I could win if I gape \Nmy mouth when I throw rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:41.83,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Except I totally heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:43.34,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.54,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:47.89,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:49.26,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:53.47,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,So what if I make a "hnnngh" \Nface and throw rock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:55.60,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:14:59.14,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.90,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,How, how?! What gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.40,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:08.24,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,How about this, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:10.90,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:13.00,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,gone void.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:16.74,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.12,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,I win! I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:21.12,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.96,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:25.13,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:29.20,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.27,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:31.84,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:34.55,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,You can take a break if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:40.56,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,I'll ask you for help with the shed later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:43.40,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Why not enjoy the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.90,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,You might meet someone special.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.29,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Someone special, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:02.78,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,She's just asleep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:07.69,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:09.74,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,How is it so safe out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:15.04,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.39,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.54,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:38.20,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.97,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:43.21,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,Why are you holding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.98,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,A-Are you going to have your way with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.54,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,Please go slow at first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:52.16,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,So I can be aggressive eventually?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:54.17,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:00.86,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,Takahara Hairi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:02.14,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,Weird name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:04.39,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You can take it up with my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:06.50,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,And you're going through your grandma's stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.71,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,You'll be here a long time then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:09.84,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,For a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.58,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Do you have to be so blatantly \Ncreeped out by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:15.65,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm not that emotionally secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:17.69,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,How could I {\i1}not{\i0} be creeped out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:20.08,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,You attacked me in my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.23,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I never attacked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:25.10,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,Anyway, if you see me \Nsleeping, leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.22,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:28.26,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,It's two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:29.91,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,I'm late for work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:32.18,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,Inari! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:32.95,Default,Inari,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:39.30,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It's two?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.16,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,How did she know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.94,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I need a change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:51.88,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,The sea swallows everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:55.74,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Spending summer in an unfamiliar land,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:57.15,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,all my little worries just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:06.89,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Summer is always cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:09.92,Default,Kido's Grandmother,0,0,0,,He's really taking it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.14,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:32.15,Default,Ryouichi,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be dressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:33.15,Default,Ryouichi,0,0,0,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:34.36,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It's dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:38.43,Default,Ryouichi,0,0,0,,That freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.66,Default,Ryouichi,0,0,0,,She shot at me without warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:41.28,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shot{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:43.15,Default,Miki,0,0,0,,You there, flasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:47.43,Default,Miki,0,0,0,,You are not to be undressed \Noutside of the bathing area!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:50.29,Default,Miki,0,0,0,,Dress yourself and turn yourself\Nin immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:52.92,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:54.49,Default,Ryouichi,0,0,0,,A shirtless hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:55.75,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:18:59.92,Default,Ryouichi,0,0,0,,Run for your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:01.18,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:09.89,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:11.85,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Welcome b—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:14.77,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Wh-What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:16.82,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.07,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Why are you half naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.00,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:21.57,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Half naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.86,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Is this some custom on the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:27.83,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:29.29,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:32.46,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,I saw a half naked man yesterday too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:34.78,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Oh, the shirtless hunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:35.72,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Shirtless hunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:37.46,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.55,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Forget I mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:42.02,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Just hurry up and get dressed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:43.98,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.14,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Takahara-san...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.14,0:19:47.11,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,You got a delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:47.64,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fax-.35\fs10\pos(604.15,194.389)\frz325.8\c&H816BB9&\3c&HE1E2E3&\4c&H967F68&\b1}Noichigo {\c&H967F68&}100%
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:47.64,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fax-.35\fs10\c&H60A362&\3c&HE1E2E3&\4c&H7660A0&\b1\pos(450.656,299.522)\frz325}Noichigo {\c&H7660A0&}100%
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:50.14,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Is it from home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:01.57,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Were you on the swim team?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:02.66,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:04.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,The swim shorts club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.95,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,There's no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:11.37,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Just ask Kyouko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:16.12,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Kyouko-san, what's a swim shorts club?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:26.72,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Please, Takahara-san! Kyouko-san \Njust made a weird face, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:27.76,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:29.72,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Takahara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:32.24,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Takahara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:14.50,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Not bad, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:15.40,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What part?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:19.92,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, I guess I said that out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.94,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Are you lost again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.13,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.36,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,What, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:30.39,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Dosu—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:33.03,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Listen, you need to extend \Nyour arm as far as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:35.33,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Once it's out, hold it there for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:38.18,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,That'll make a big difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:37.29,Main - Top,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:39.24,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Okay, bye!

